These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
There are 3 different nationalities: spanish, indian, german
The people have 3 different hobbies: gardening, camping, puzzles
1. the spanish is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##3
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is the indian##1
4. the german is on the far left##1
5. the person who's hobby is camping is the person who's hobby is camping##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Nationality   | german | spanish | indian |
| Hobby    | camping    | puzzles | gardening |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: family, time-travel, disaster
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: trance, folk, electronic
1. the person watching family movies is on the far right##1
2. the fan of folk is in an even position##4
3. the fan of electronic is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
4. the fan of folk is the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Movie-Genre       | time-travel | disaster | family |
| Music-Genre   | electronic    | folk     | trance        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, pall-mall, cain
The people have 3 different jobs:  chef, paramedic, scientist
1. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the chef##1
2. the paramedic is on the left of the chef##1
3. the pall-mall-smoker is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Cigar         | cain     | pall-mall | bluemaster |
| Job   | paramedic | chef     | scientist  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
3 different games are played: billiard, domino, go
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, bolivar, fonseca
1. the person playing domino is the bolivar-smoker##1
2. the person playing billiard is the fonseca-smoker##1
3. the person playing domino is in an even position##4
4. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Game   | go | domino  | billiard  |
| Cigar         | game  | bolivar | fonseca |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, fanta, iced-tea
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, van, airplane
1. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person driving the scooter##2
2. the person drinking fanta is in an odd position##4
3. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Beverage         | soy-milk   | iced-tea | fanta    |
| Transport   | van | airplane     | scooter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
City: san-francisco, venice, rome
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, chaman, montecristo
1. the person traveling to san-francisco is the chaman-smoker##1
2. the montecristo-smoker is the person traveling to venice##1
3. the person traveling to venice is in an odd position##4
4. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the montecristo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| City   | venice | rome | san-francisco   |
| Cigar   | montecristo     | bolivar    | chaman |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, whist, snooker
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, bike, helicopter
1. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
2. the person playing mah-jongg is between the person driving the helicopter and the person playing snooker##2
3. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person playing whist##1
4. the person driving the taxi is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| Game   | snooker | mah-jongg | whist |
| Transport           | bike         | taxi         | helicopter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: grey, blue, amber
The people use 3 different means of transport: train, jet-ski, ship
1. the person driving the train is between the person driving the jet-ski and the person who likes grey##2
2. the person driving the ship is in an odd position##4
3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person who likes amber##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Color   | blue | amber | grey |
| Transport    | jet-ski    | train | ship     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
3 different games are played: billiard, bridge, chess
3 different pets are kept: bird, pony, ferret
1. the owner of the ferret is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
3. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
4. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Game   | chess   | bridge  | billiard  |
| Pet         | ferret | pony | bird |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-10::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: techno, hip-hop, disco
The people have 3 different jobs:  nurse, firefighter, manager
1. the nurse is on the right of the fan of disco##1
2. the manager is in an even position##4
3. the manager is on the right of the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | techno    | disco      | hip-hop |
| Job       | firefighter | manager | nurse   |

