.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-11::.
There 3 different types of food: pumpkin, kale, cauliflower
House: victorian, cape-cod, modern
1. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person eating kale##1
2. the victorian house is the person eating pumpkin##1
3. the modern house is the person eating cauliflower##1
4. the person eating cauliflower is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| Food         | kale | cauliflower | pumpkin |
| House   | cape-cod | modern   | victorian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-12::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: reggae, salsa, electronic
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, poker, snooker
1. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
2. the fan of reggae is the person playing snooker##1
3. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
4. the person playing snooker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | salsa | reggae |
| Game     | poker     | mah-jongg   | snooker        |

