.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-13::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, tea, sprite
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, december, may
1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is the person drinking tea##1
3. the person drinking sprite is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |
| Beverage   | sprite  | water | tea   |
| Birthday         | december | may   | march |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, november, february
There are 3 different favourite colors: red, apricot, emerald
1. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person who's birthday is in november and the person who likes apricot##2
2. the person who's birthday is in november is in an odd position##4
3. the person who likes apricot is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who likes red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Birthday   | november | february | april |
| Color     | red    | emerald  | apricot   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-15::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, baccarat, ritmeester
There are 3 different favourite beverages: tea, lemonade, coffee
1. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the ritmeester-smoker##3
4. the ritmeester-smoker is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |
| Cigar   | blend  | ritmeester     | baccarat |
| Beverage   | lemonade | tea | coffee    |

