.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-17::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: soccer, weightlifting, cycling
City: prague, nizza, paris
1. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
2. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
3. the person traveling to prague is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |
| Sport   | soccer | cycling | weightlifting    |
| City           | nizza     | paris  | prague |

