.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-18::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daisy, balloon-flower, dahlia
City: edinburgh, hannover, hamburg
1. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
2. the person who growsdaisy is in the middle##1
3. the person who growsdahlia is the person traveling to hannover##1
4. the person traveling to edinburgh is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Flower         | dahlia | daisy   | balloon-flower |
| City   | hannover   | edinburgh | hamburg      |

