.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-19::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: sunflower, lily, iris
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, december, august
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the person who growssunflower##3
2. the person who growssunflower is in an odd position##4
3. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who growslily##1
4. the person who growslily is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |    3     |
| Flower      | sunflower | lily | iris |
| Birthday   | december   | august          | march |

