.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: reggae, electronic, blues
City: hannover, london, san-francisco
1. the person traveling to san-francisco is in an odd position##4
2. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the fan of blues##1
3. the fan of blues is in an even position##4
4. the person traveling to london is on the right of the fan of electronic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |
| Music-Genre     | electronic  | blues   | reggae |
| City   | san-francisco | london | hannover       |

 